{"tid":2489970,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台：良好棉花發展協會據報刪走去年抵制新疆棉花的聲明","createTime":"2021-04-15T09:19:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T09:47:07.000Z","uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1411ef5690e688653298d8a6c1d6645902f95b8a","tid":2489970,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:19:19.000Z","msg":"中國環球電視網CGTN報道，良好棉花發展協會BCI的網站，已刪走去年發表抵制新疆棉花的聲明。<br />\n<br />\n協會在去年發表的聲明中，指控新疆出現事實上並不存在的「強迫勞動」，藉故停止在新疆維吾爾自治區的所有活動。有內地網民早前重提H&amp;M等國際品牌，關注新疆強迫勞動的問題，隨即引起內地官方媒體和民眾，聲討這些國際品牌的行為，多個網購平台將H&amp;M產品下架，多個導航地圖程式亦遮蓋H&amp;M商店的地址。<br />\n<br />\n不過，BCI上海代表處其後發表聲明，重申從未在新疆發現強迫勞動事件，企業的行為與他們無關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1585961-20210415.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1585961-20210415.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sIoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=665ff523\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1585961-20210415.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=353633b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1585961-20210415.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"2f768781f20e49ac6a284ccbe681fa0c16229794","tid":2489970,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://megapx.dcard.tw/v1/images/e5f033b3-b369-4b66-8b40-2a37665f1fa1/encode/640.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmegapx.dcard.tw%2Fv1%2Fimages%2Fe5f033b3-b369-4b66-8b40-2a37665f1fa1%2Fencode%2F640.webp&h=69273719&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c47a14568e62fd459c0b88b87ecdcb41be1d10b","tid":2489970,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:20:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/e5f033b3-b369-4b66-8b40-2a37665f1fa1/full.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg